\"}},\"layout\":\"constrained\",\"width\":1024,\"height\":683},\"alt\":\"\",\"className\":\"wp-image-2560 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper\",\"data-wp-inline-image\":\"1\"}</script><figcaption>The toggle and loop create a quick release mechanism for anchoring the clothesline.</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3>Step 5</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>At the other end of the line, attach the line to your second anchor point by wrapping the end of the prusik loop with the carabiner around your anchor and clipping the carabiner back onto the prusik. Holding the free end of the clothesline, pull the line tight. Push the prusik knot forward to catch your progress. Pull the line tight and push the knot forward until it’s as tight as you’d like. It can help to throw the end of the line you are pulling over a branch so that the direction of pull is vertical instead of horizontal.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div data-gatsby-image-wrapper=\"\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;display:inline-block;vertical-align:top\" class=\"gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper-constrained wp-image-2561 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper\" data-reactroot=\"\"><div style=\"max-width:1024px;display:block\"><img alt=\"\" role=\"presentation\" aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg height=&#x27;683&#x27; width=&#x27;1024&#x27; xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27; version=&#x27;1.1&#x27;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" style=\"max-width:100%;display:block;position:static\"/></div><div aria-hidden=\"true\" data-placeholder-image=\"\" style=\"height:100%;left:0;position:absolute;top:0;width:100%\"></div><img data-gatsby-image-ssr=\"\" data-wp-inline-image=\"2\" data-main-image=\"\" style=\"height:100%;left:0;position:absolute;top:0;transform:translateZ(0);transition:opacity 250ms linear;width:100%;will-change:opacity;opacity:0\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1024px) 1024px, 100vw\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"/_gatsby/image/e42a0386c8674b96ee627728e54282b3/337afbe5a0d6cb6ca86467eea89b43e0/IMG_1619-scaled-1.jpg?u=https%3A%2F%2Flucashubbard.com%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F09%2FIMG_1619-scaled-1.jpg&amp;a=w%3D256%26h%3D171%26fm%3Djpg%26q%3D90&amp;cd=2021-09-06T20%3A56%3A00\" data-srcset=\"/_gatsby/image/e42a0386c8674b96ee627728e54282b3/337afbe5a0d6cb6ca86467eea89b43e0/IMG_1619-scaled-1.jpg?u=https%3A%2F%2Flucashubbard.com%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F09%2FIMG_1619-scaled-1.jpg&amp;a=w%3D256%26h%3D171%26fm%3Djpg%26q%3D90&amp;cd=2021-09-06T20%3A56%3A00 256w,/_gatsby/image/e42a0386c8674b96ee627728e54282b3/31792159b8913c18d5797cb400c851d4/IMG_1619-scaled-1.jpg?u=https%3A%2F%2Flucashubbard.com%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F09%2FIMG_1619-scaled-1.jpg&amp;a=w%3D512%26h%3D341%26fm%3Djpg%26q%3D90&amp;cd=2021-09-06T20%3A56%3A00 512w,/_gatsby/image/e42a0386c8674b96ee627728e54282b3/c63028dc58fb9e40beb4fcfe19ba2cd8/IMG_1619-scaled-1.jpg?u=https%3A%2F%2Flucashubbard.com%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F09%2FIMG_1619-scaled-1.jpg&amp;a=w%3D1024%26h%3D683%26fm%3Djpg%26q%3D90&amp;cd=2021-09-06T20%3A56%3A00 1024w,/_gatsby/image/e42a0386c8674b96ee627728e54282b3/538bbe1427eb7514d4f6e7cdacce2380/IMG_1619-scaled-1.jpg?u=https%3A%2F%2Flucashubbard.com%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F09%2FIMG_1619-scaled-1.jpg&amp;a=w%3D2048%26h%3D1366%26fm%3Djpg%26q%3D90&amp;cd=2021-09-06T20%3A56%3A00 2048w\" alt=\"\"/><noscript><img data-gatsby-image-ssr=\"\" data-wp-inline-image=\"2\" data-main-image=\"\" style=\"height:100%;left:0;position:absolute;top:0;transform:translateZ(0);transition:opacity 250ms linear;width:100%;will-change:opacity;opacity:0\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1024px) 1024px, 100vw\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/_gatsby/image/e42a0386c8674b96ee627728e54282b3/337afbe5a0d6cb6ca86467eea89b43e0/IMG_1619-scaled-1.jpg?u=https%3A%2F%2Flucashubbard.com%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F09%2FIMG_1619-scaled-1.jpg&amp;a=w%3D256%26h%3D171%26fm%3Djpg%26q%3D90&amp;cd=2021-09