24w,/_gatsby/image/bbc1e14de8dca551cbcd8a4d943c07ec/538bbe1427eb7514d4f6e7cdacce2380/IMG_1620-scaled-1.jpg?u=https%3A%2F%2Flucashubbard.com%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F09%2FIMG_1620-scaled-1.jpg&a=w%3D2048%26h%3D1366%26fm%3Djpg%26q%3D90&cd=2021-09-06T20%3A56%3A14 2048w\",\"sizes\":\"(min-width: 1024px) 1024px, 100vw\"}},\"layout\":\"constrained\",\"width\":1024,\"height\":683},\"alt\":\"\",\"className\":\"wp-image-2562 inline-gatsby-image-wrapper\",\"data-wp-inline-image\":\"3\"}</script><figcaption>The prusik knot holding tension.</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Step 6</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>To take the line down, just pull out the toggle and wrap up the line. Taking care of a clothesline is just like taking can of any other rope. <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Aqt1ntSVjJA\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">This video</a> may help. You may want to make a spool to wrap your clothesline onto. Keeping your clothesline put away, when not in use, will ensure it lasts for years to come. It also keeps the line clean, so it won’t soil the clothes hung on it.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>To Wrap It All Up</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Line drying clothes is indeed one of the most simple and elegant ways we can put ambient sunlight and wind to use. By making the above adaptations, I’ve made it much easier to ditch the clothes dryer. I would have solved my problem sooner if I had not thought of a clothesline as a piece of infrastructure that always stands erect in the yard. While some people seem to make that work (<a href=\"https://www.practicallyfunctional.com/diy-pulley-clothesline/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" title=\"How To Make A DIY Pulley Clothesline\">see pulley clothes lines</a>), I’ve had greater success by thinking of the clothesline as a tool that comes out only when it’s time to use it.</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"id":"cG9zdDoyNTU2","slug":"how-to-make-a-natural-fiber-clothesline-that-stays-tight-and-wont-break","__params":{"slug":"how-to-make-a-natural-fiber-clothesline-that-stays-tight-and-wont-break"}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3159585216"]}